<div class="endorsement-page shelf-page">

<p class="essay-back"><a href="/writing/">← Back to The Library</a></p>

  <div class="endorsement-layout shelf-layout">

    <aside class="endorsement-nav shelf-nav">
      <h1>Military Chaplaincy</h1>  

      <p class="endorsement-subtitle shelf-subtitle">
        Reflections, essays, issue papers, briefs, and submissions related to military chaplaincy,
        religious accommodation, personnel policy, and public service.
      </p>

      <div class="shelf-nav-group browse-nav-group">
        <a class="browse-nav-link" href="/military-chaplaincy/reflections-and-essays/">
          Reflections &amp; Essays
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="shelf-nav-group browse-nav-group">
        <a class="browse-nav-link" href="/military-chaplaincy/issues-and-analysis/">
          Issues &amp; Analysis
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="shelf-nav-group browse-nav-group active">
        <a class="browse-nav-link" href="/military-chaplaincy/briefs-and-submissions/">
          Briefs &amp; Submissions
        </a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="endorsement-main shelf-main">

      <section class="endorsement-feature shelf-feature panel">
        <h2>Featured Works</h2>

        {% for item in collections.featuredMilitaryChaplaincy %}
          <div class="endorsement-feature-item">

            <h3>
              <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
            </h3>

            {% if item.data.subtitle %}
              <p class="endorsement-feature-subtitle">
                {{ item.data.subtitle }}
              </p>
            {% endif %}

            {% if item.data.feature_blurb or item.data.feature_excerpt %}
              <div class="endorsement-feature-excerpt shelf-feature-excerpt">
                <p>{{ item.data.feature_blurb or item.data.feature_excerpt }}</p>
              </div>
            {% endif %}

          </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </section>

      <section class="endorsement-howto shelf-howto panel">
        <h2>About This Section</h2>

        <p>
          This shelf gathers my work related to military chaplaincy, religious accommodation,
          personnel policy, ecclesiastical endorsement, and the institutional practice of
          supporting the free exercise of religion within the armed forces.
        </p>

        <p>
          Some documents are reflective essays intended for a broad audience. Others are issue
          papers, briefing documents, formal submissions, or policy analyses prepared for
          denominational leaders, governmental agencies, advocacy organizations, and professional
          colleagues. Together they represent an ongoing body of work shaped by decades of service
          as a military chaplain, endorsed clergy, and institutional leader.
        </p>

      </section>

    </main>

  </div>
</div>

